---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Our commitment to your privacy.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 prose prose-blue">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last Updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US')}</p>
    
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We do not collect personal information unless you voluntarily provide it. Like most websites, we may collect non-identifying information such as browser type, IP address, and pages visited to improve our services.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">2. Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use cookies to understand how you interact with our site and to provide a better user experience. You can choose to disable cookies through your browser settings.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">3. Third-Party Links</h2>
    <p>Our website contains links to external sites (such as ClickBank products). We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these third-party sites.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">4. Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
    <p>We are an affiliate marketer. When you click on links to various products on this site and make a purchase, this can result in a commission that is credited to this site.</p>
  </div>
</MainLayout>